quran[10{c,v,t}:
10,79,"aur firaon ne ( apne admion se ) kaha ke “har maahir fun jadugar ko mere paas haazir karo """
10,80,"jab jaadoo gir aa gay to moose ne un se kaha “jo kuch tumhe phenkna hai phenko """
10,81,"phir jab unhon ne apne آAnnchar pheink diye to moose ne kaha “ih jo kuch tum ne phenka hai yeh jaadoo hai, Allah abhi isay baatil kiye deta hai, mfsdon ke kaam ko Allah sdhrne nahi deta"
10,82,"aur Allah apne farmanoon se haq ko haq kar dekhata hai, khuwa mujrimon ko woh kitna hi nagawaar ho """
10,83,"( phir dekho ke ) moose ko is ki qoum mein se chand nojawanon ke siwa kisi ne nah maana, firaon ke dar se aur khud apni qoum ke sir Bar Awerda logon ke dar se ( jinhein khauf tha ke ) firaon un ko azaab mein mubtala kere ga aur waqea yeh hai ke firaon zameen mein ghalba rakhta tha aur woh unn logon mein se tha jo kisi hadd par ruktay nahi hain"
10,84,"moose ne apni qoum se kaha ke “logo, agar tum waqai Allah par imaan rakhtay ho to is par bharosa karo agar musalman ho """
10,85,"unhon ne jawab diya “hm ne Allah hi par bharosa kya, ae hamaray rab, hamein zalim logon ke liye fitnah nah bana"
10,86,"aur apni rehmat se hum ko kafiroon se nijaat day """
10,87,"aur hum ne moose aur is ke bhai ko ishara kya ke “misar mein chand makaan apni qoum ke liye muhayya karo aur apne un makanon ko qiblatehra lau aur namaz qaim karo aur ahal imaan ko basharat day do """
10,88,"moose ne dua ki “ayhamaray rab, to ne firaon aur is ke sardaro ko duniya ki zindagi mein zeenat aur amwal se Nawaz rakha hai ae rab, kya yeh is liye hai ke woh logon ko teri raah se buhtka-ayn? ae rab, un ke maal ghaarat kar day aur un ke dilon par aisi mohar kar day ke imaan nah layein jab taq dard naak azaab nah dekh len """
